Features not yet supported:
1. custom sounds
2. sensors:
   2a. see dot/dash
   2b. hear clap
   2c. picked up (isBeingShaken() could be an alternative?)
   2d. stuck
3. set wheel speed left/right separately (use turning to degree as an alternative)
4. turn to voice / look towards voice (directional hearing)
5. add offset value to tilt sensors

